Title: Y'all are sleeping on HTTP/3
Description:
Wake up call This post is about HTTP/3 and QUIC. If you don’t know what that is, there are many, many, many, many, many, many, many good resources that will get you up to speed. I’m writing this post to enlighten people on what has been happening in the last few years.
All major browsers support HTTP/3 now.
Most major cloud providers support HTTP/3 now.
Most major load balancers support HTTP/3 now.
